Please follow the following steps

1. type make on the command line to build both client and server

2. Run the server by typing ./stringServer

3. It should print out SERVER_ADDRESS <addr> and SERVER_PORT <port>

4. On another terminal, set the environment variable using the <addr> and <port> you got from the server
	export SERVER_ADDRESS="<addr>"
	export SERVER_PORT="<port>"

5. Run the client by typing ./stringClient

6. Type the input and the translation will come up in couple second

7. Press ctrl D to terminate the client

Note that server will keep running and are able to take up to 5 clients simultanuously 
